&lt;p&gt;The successful applicants will assist in the overall delivery of care to patients within the Primary Care department of HMP Garth. You will be responsible for the assessment of care needs and the development, implementation and evaluation of programmes of care. The post holder will at all times comply with the NMC Code of Conduct, relevant legislation policies and procedures.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Healthcare services operate 7 days a week, 24 hours a day, and the successful applicants would need to be flexible in their approach to meeting the demands of the service.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt; &lt;/p&gt;
